         <abstract id="aspace_c4379b55b6d9c7c3bdf0500b37b2d710">The collection consists of commemorative artifacts and printed materials created to celebrate British Royal Jubilees, in particular, the Golden Jubilee of Queen Elizabeth II.</abstract>
    
