      <prefercite id="aspace_3d030259141af80239d916460b4f0aaa">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Royal Coronation and Jubilee Collection (MS 1812). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_5d578a3b84a9fdeb4941174c3773ebde">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged alphabetically by name of monarch.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_35950ad25f7cfaedb231391b17e9e3dd">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of commemorative artifacts and printed materials created to celebrate British Royal Jubilees, in particular, the Golden Jubilee of Queen Elizabeth II.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
